<h2 id="org9f8734d">Cut</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org9f8734d">
<p>
David Deutsch
in the <a href="BeginningOfInfinity.html#ID-79681BB2-0968-4644-8EA5-905DB31B28AD">Beginning of Infinity</a>, defines the supernatural as things that
people &#x2013; universal explainers and constructors &#x2013; are qualitatively
unable to understand. Deutsch assumes the explicability of nature:
"regularities have explanations; the world is not supernatural".
</p>
